00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:13.919
The spirit beasts escaped.

00:03:13.960 --> 00:03:15.439
You govern poorly yourself,

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:16.879
so why blame me?

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.560
What does that have to do with me?

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:27.280
That woman at the Paramount
slashed at you.

00:03:27.719 --> 00:03:29.439
I taught her a lesson for you.

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:32.719
I sealed her in the dream disc.

00:03:32.719 --> 00:03:34.120
She will die soon.

00:03:34.520 --> 00:03:35.759
How amusing.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:37.919
