00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:40.159
My good brother.

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.439
Li Motong.

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:47.680
I have sealed her in the dream disc.

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:49.680
If you want to free her,

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.960
