on purpose using my sister's voice?

00:04:26.439 --> 00:04:27.480
You want to kill me?

00:04:28.839 --> 00:04:31.199
I have no interest in human lives.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.390
We are both trapped
inside the dream disc.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.439
If you want to leave here alive,

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:38.639
you must work with me.

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:40.399
You monsters.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.240
You killed my sister.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:44.399
I will never cooperate with you.

00:04:44.399 --> 00:04:45.639
If you refuse to work with me,

00:04:46.079 --> 00:04:47.439
then you can only die.

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:48.839
Even if it means death,

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:50.920
I will never stand with you.

00:04:51.839 --> 00:04:52.639
Miss Lu.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.600
